trans-unit.source: Creates and populates an <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"></xref> that is used by the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.MetadataStore"></xref> to provide attribute lookup and registration.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter og fyller ut en <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"> </xref> som brukes av den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.MetadataStore"> </xref> angi attributtet oppslag og registrering.

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>, <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>, and <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddTable%2A> to populate the builder, then call <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.CreateTable%2A> to acquire an <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> containing the desired collection of attributes.
trans-unit.target: Bruk <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>, <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>, og <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddTable%2A>for å fylle ut verktøyet kalle <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.CreateTable%2A>å hente en <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>som inneholder den ønskede samlingen attributter.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.CreateTable%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddTable%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Specifies a callback that will be invoked when metadata for the given type is needed.
trans-unit.target: Angir en tilbakeringing som vil bli startet når metadataene for den angitte typen er nødvendig.

trans-unit.source: The first time an <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> returned by <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.CreateTable%2A> is queried for attributes for `type`, `callback` is called to provide the metadata information.
trans-unit.target: Første gang en <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>ble returnert av <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.CreateTable%2A>forespørres for attributter for `type`, `callback` kalles for å gi metadatainformasjon.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.CreateTable%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>

trans-unit.source: The type for which the callback will provide metadata.
trans-unit.target: Typen som gir tilbakeringing metadata.

trans-unit.source: The callback method.
trans-unit.target: Tilbakekallingsmetoden.

trans-unit.source: Adds the contents of the provided attributes to this builder.
trans-unit.target: Legger til innholdet i de angitte attributtene i denne builder.

trans-unit.source: If an attribute conflicts with another attribute already included in the builder, the last attribute added replaces previous attributes.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en attributtet er i konflikt med et annet attributt allerede inkludert i verktøyet, erstatter det siste attributtet legges til forrige attributter.

trans-unit.source: When building a large attribute table, use <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A> to defer the work of creating attributes until they are needed.
trans-unit.target: Når du bygger en stor attributtet tabell, kan du bruke <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>Utsettelse arbeidet for å opprette attributter før de trengs.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>

trans-unit.source: Creates an attribute table that contains all of the attribute definitions provided through <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes*> calls.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en attributtet tabell som inneholder alle attributtet definisjonene leveres gjennom <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes*>kall.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes*>

trans-unit.source: The table is a snapshot of the current state of the attribute builder; any attributes added by subsequent <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A> calls are not included in the table.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen er et øyeblikksbilde av den gjeldende tilstanden til attributtet builder; Noen attributter som er lagt til av etterfølgende <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>anrop ikke er inkludert i tabellen.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>

trans-unit.source: If callback methods were used to declare attributes, those methods will not be evaluated during CreateTable.
trans-unit.target: Hvis tilbakeringing metoder ble brukt til å deklarere attributter, evalueres ikke disse metodene under CreateTable.

trans-unit.source: Instead, the table will contain those callbacks and will evaluate them as needed.
trans-unit.target: I stedet tabellen inneholder de tilbakeringinger og vil bli evaluert etter behov.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"></xref> that can be passed to the metadata store.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"> </xref> som kan sendes til butikken metadata.

trans-unit.source: Verifies that the attribute table that is being built contains valid attribute information.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollerer at tabellen attributtet som bygges inneholder gyldig attributtinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: Some overrides of <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>cannot validate that values passed to their parameters represent valid members on classes.
trans-unit.target: Noen overstyring av <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>kan ikke validere at verdiene som er sendt til sine parametere representerer gyldig medlemmer i klasser.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>

trans-unit.source: ValidateTable verifies that all custom attribute information corresponds to actual members.
trans-unit.target: ValidateTable bekrefter at all informasjon på egendefinert attributt tilsvarer faktiske medlemmene.

trans-unit.source: This method can take a long time to complete and is not recommended unless validation is explicitly needed.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kan ta lang tid å fullføre og anbefales ikke hvis validering eksplisitt er nødvendig.

trans-unit.source: the state of the table is invalid.
trans-unit.target: Status for tabellen er ugyldig.
